00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:54.880
Saya tidak akan mengampuni dia!

00:01:55.520 --> 00:01:56.600
Biarkan dia datang.

00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:58.000
Aku akan menguliti itu!

00:01:58.200 --> 00:01:59.240
Kavya.

00:02:01.360 --> 00:02:02.400
Kavya.

00:02:03.840 --> 00:02:04.920
